        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 28 at 2:55PM MDT until July 28 at 3:45PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 255 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 7 miles northwest of
Hobson, or 11 miles southeast of Stanford, moving northeast at 20
mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage to
roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Hobson, Ackley Lake State Park, Moccasin, and Benchland.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
